title: Non-invasive Ventilation (NIV)
description: NIV has two major modes of supplying ventilatory support, namely, continuous positive airway pressure (CPAP) and bilevel positive airway pressure (BiPAP).

title: Invasive Mechanical Ventilation (MV)
description: MV has two major modes of supplying ventilatory support, namely, continuous positive airway pressure (CPAP) and bilevel positive airway pressure (BiPAP).
